column14: As a customer, i want to make payment so that i can pay the amount
As a customer , i wish to log in to the system , so that i can trace all the item previously i purchase .
As a customer, I want the system can do member registration so that I can subscribe for the information of updates and promotion.
As a customer, I can check out myself bill so that I can make payment
As a customer, I want the system can add item to the cart , so I can purchase all the item I want easily.
As a customer, I want the system can update the item cart, so that I can make any changes when I make any mistake.
As a admin,i wish that the system able to add new product ,so that new item can added in the product list
As  a admin , i wish that the system able edit product,so that the product up to date.
As a admin , i wish that system able to remove product , so that the item will deleted in product list
As an Admin, I can know the available quantity of each stock
As an Admin, I can know how many order has been process and deleted in each day, month and year
As a customer , i wish the system  allow me to delete my account , so that i won't be member as i wish to cancel my member
As a customer, i wish to able to update my membership detail , so that the information in the database is up-to-date
As a customer, I can generate receipt so that I can prove that the bill has been paid
As a customer, I want the system can cancel the purchase cart, so that I can delete the cart when I change my mind.
As a member, i wan the system able do feedback so that  i can improve the system more better that before
